text: Birger Nilsen (July 23, 1881 - June 1981) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1981 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kragerø
